<h2>Why Vehicle Graphics?</h2>
<p>Vehicle graphics are the most cost-effective form of local advertising available. A single branded van generates <strong>30,000–70,000 impressions per day</strong> in Chicago traffic. Unlike digital ads or billboards, there's no recurring cost — one investment that works for 5–7 years.</p>
<p>For small businesses, vehicle graphics are often the first step into fleet branding. Simple lettering and logo decals can be applied in under a day, delivering immediate brand visibility on every job, every commute, and every errand.</p>

<h2>Materials</h2>
<p>We use only premium materials from <strong>Avery Dennison</strong> and <strong>3M</strong>. Cast vinyl conforms to curves and rivets without lifting, and is rated for 5–7 years outdoor durability in Chicago weather. Cut vinyl lettering lasts 7–10 years. See our <a href="/materials/" style="color:var(--gold)">Materials Guide →</a></p>
